      "column": "left",
      "text": "Pehz nahze tee Wehſtneſcht atkaſ/ un faẓẓija: Tā runna Ben-Adads/un faḳḳa: Eṣ gaṇefinu pee tew fuhtijs/ un lizzisfaẓẓiht: Tawu Sudrabu un tawu Seltn/ un tawas Seewasun tawus Behrnus buhs tewman doht.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 6,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Bet rihtu ap fcho Laiknfuhtischu es fawus Kalpus peetew/ ka tee tawu Namnu/ untawu Kalpu Namnu iṣmekle/un wiṣṣ/ kaṣ tur skaists irrpreekſch twahm Azzin/to buhs teem Rohkā nemit/ un aisnest.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 7,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tad fa-aizinaja tas Isra-eka Kehniſsch wiṣṣas SemmesWezzajus/ un faẓẓija: Nemmeet jelle wehrā/ un redseet/ kaſchiṣ taunu mekle. Jo tas bijpee man fuhtijs pehz mannahmSeewahm/ un pehz manneemBehrneem/ un pehz mannu Sudrabu un Seltu/ un es tam tonē eṣinu aiṣleedsis.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 8,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Bet wiṣṣee Wezzajee/ unwiṣṣi Landis faẓẓija us wiṣṣu:Ne paklauti/ un ne dohd tamWaknu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 9,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tad faẓẓija wiṣṣch us Ben-Adada Wehſtneſcheem: Sakkajtmannain Kungam tam Kehni-am: Wiṣṣu/ par fo tu pirnuReisi pee tawu Kalpu fuhtijs/griḅbu es darriht/ bet fcho Lee-tu es ne warru darriht. Tadnogahje tee Wehſtneṣchi/un atfaẓ-zija wiṇṇam to Wahṛdu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 10,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un Ben-Adads fuhtijapee wiṇṇa/ un liḳke faẓẓiht:Latd man tee Deewi fcha un tadarra/ ja Samarias Pihſchligann buhs preekſch wiṣṣeimLandim/ kaṣ pakkat man irr/ kaikātrs piṣnu Sanju nemim.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 11,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Bet tas Israėta Kehniſschatbildeja/ un faẓẓija: Runnajeetta/ kaṣ aprbrunnrojahs/ tas latne leelijahs/ ittin ka tas/ kaṣBruknas irr nohṣt lizzis.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 12,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Kad nu tas fcho Wahṛduosirdeja/ jo wiṣṣch deḣre ar teemKehniṣsem Teltis/ tad faẓẓjawiṣṣch us faweem Kalpein:Taiſajtees/ un tee taiṣijahs prettto Piṣṣahtu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 13,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un raugi/ weens Pra-weets nahze pee Akabu to Isra-eka Kehniṣu/un faẓẓija: Ta faḳ-ka tas KUNGS: Effi tu wiṣṣfscho leeln Pulku redsejs? raugi/es dohſchu to schodeen tawā Roh-kā/ ka tu atsiḥsti man effaim toKUNGU.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 14,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un Akabs faẓẓija: Zaurko? tad faẓẓija wiṣṣch : Ta faḳkatas KUNGS: Zaur to Sem-mes-Waldneeku Puſcheem. Unwiṣṣch faẓẓija: Kaṣ to Rauſcha-nu eekahks? tad faẓẓija wiṣṣch:Tn pats.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 15,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tad taiṣija wiṣṣch toSemmes-Waldneeku Puſchus/to bija diviſimts trihṣdefinitcsun divi. Un pehz teem lihdsī-naja wiṣṣch wiṣṣus Landis/wiṣ-fus Israėta Behrnus/ to bijaseptin tuhḱtoschi.\n"
